text:
We’ve been visiting this chicken rice stall since its earlier locations at Hougang and Beauty World, and it never disappoints. The rice is always served warm and fragrant, which IMO makes the meal particularly comforting. The white chicken is consistently smooth and tender, and their zesty, aromatic chili sauce is a perfect complement.

This stall definitely stands out as one of my favorite neighbourhood chicken rice spots!

I love the chicken char siew and roasted pork because it’s so soft and yummy even the egg and offal are so yummy too This stall’s chicken rice is the best I have ever eaten and will make people eat again👍👍👍
